snippet.title: AMBER HEARD A POSSIBLE NEW DISNEY PRINCESS?
snippet.description:
From the rumors of her being Sue Storm and many other characters in other places. This has got to be the most weirdest one, and for good reason. To me, she doesn't really have that 'vibe' going for her. More of a villainess type of vibe if you ask me.
